			RETURN
			"data:image/svg+xml;utf8," & 
			"<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>" & 
			    -- Fond incliné (ici neutre à 0° pour varier ou -10° pour uniformiser)
			    "<rect x='2' y='2' width='20' height='20' rx='6' fill='" & Couleur & "' fill-opacity='0.12' transform='rotate(5 12 12)' />" & 
			    -- Tes lignes de graphique
			    "<g fill='none' stroke='" & Couleur & "' stroke-width='2.5' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'>" & 
			        "<line x1='18' y1='17' x2='18' y2='10'></line>" & 
			        "<line x1='12' y1='17' x2='12' y2='7'></line>" & 
			        "<line x1='6' y1='17' x2='6' y2='13'></line>" & 
			    "</g>" & 
			"</svg>"
			```
